Follow your dreams.” And he did, all the way to this swaggering, staggering victory, one which all of cycling hopes will help mark him out as a fitting new champion, clean, inspiring and breaking new international barriers, for cycling’s post-Armstrong age. “This is one yellow jersey which will stand the test of time,” he promised on the podium.
